*THIS IS NOT A REMASTER BUT THE ORIGINAL VINYL AS IT WAS MEANT TO SOUND*

You know the record label called Victory Records ? This is their rarest release ever, a 7" EP by the Chicago-based Straight Edge band "Insight", issued back in 1989.

It is the 4th record issued by Victory Records (more than 300 different albums today), way before they turned a sell-out emo label !

Insight was (disbanded in early 1992) an amazing band, and songs on this EP such as Enough, Believe and Identity Crisis will forever remain classics in the sXe Hardcore circle.

This is your first and last chance to hear them !
